  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "题目给定一个仅由小写字母组成的字符串 $s$，下标从 $1$ 开始。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "有 $Q$ 次询问，每组询问给定两个数 $l$ 和 $r$，表示询问 $s_l \\sim s_r$ 这段区间中包含了多少个<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%9E%E6%96%87%E4%B8%B2/1274921\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"md-link\">回文串</a>。注意单独一个字符也算回文串。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行一个字符串 $s$，保证 $|s| \\le 5000$；",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第二行一个正整数 $Q$，保证 $1 \\le Q \\le 10^6$；",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "接下来 $Q$ 行，每行两个正整数 $l$ 和 $r$，描述一组询问。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "针对 $Q$ 组询问，分别输出对应的答案。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "caaaba\n5\n1 1\n1 4\n2 3\n4 6\n4 5",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "1\n7\n3\n4\n2",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一步：用 $O(N^2)$ 的区间 DP 预处理出 <code>is_pal[i][j]</code> 表示 $[i, j]$ 是否是回文串。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第二步：定义一个新的状态 <code>dp[i][j]</code> 表示区间 $[i, j]$ 内部的回文串<strong>总数</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "它的转移方程极其优美，利用了二维容斥原理（类似二维前缀和的思想）：<code>dp[i][j] = dp[i+1][j] + dp[i][j-1] - dp[i+1][j-1] + is_pal[i][j]</code>。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "int dp[N][N];\nbool hui[N][N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tstring s; cin >> s;\n\tint n = s.size(); s = ' ' + s;\n\tint q; cin >> q;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)hui[i][i] = hui[i][i - 1] = 1, dp[i][i] = 1;\n\tfa(len, 2, n)fa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint j = i + len - 1;\n\t\tif (j > n)break;\n\t\tif (hui[i + 1][j - 1] and s[i] == s[j])hui[i][j] = 1;\n\t\tdp[i][j] = dp[i + 1][j] + dp[i][j - 1] - dp[i + 1][j - 1] + hui[i][j];\n\t}\n\twhile (q--) {\n\t\tint l, r; cin >> l >> r;\n\t\tcout << dp[l][r] << endl;\n\t}\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
